pageContext.claim: “Congresswoman Maxine Waters, an extraordinarily low IQ person, has become, together with Nancy Pelosi, the Face of the Democrat Party. She has just called for harm to supporters, of which there are many, of the Make America Great Again movement. Be careful what you wish for Max!”
pageContext.analysis: Waters did not call for "harm" against Trump supporters. She said activists should "harass" Trump Cabinet members in public.
